Package Hospital.Schedules.Constraints.Implementation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DoctorBackToBackConstraint
    Constraints doctors so that they can only have appointments on the full hour or directly after a previous appointment (including walking time).
    NullConstraint
    This creates a fake Constraint that is always accepted.
    NurseAppointmentBackToBackConstraint
    Nurses can only have appointments directly after a previous appointment, or at a full hour
    UnmovableConstraint
    Constraints the fact that some resources can't move to the decided campus.
    WalkTimeConstraint
    Defines the constraint that every schedule needs to have enough time to walk campusses.
    WorkingHoursTimeConstraint
    Defines the constraint that appointments can only happen between 9:00 and 17:00
